1. If you do not want to read lots of stuff, just try

- run all test (30-60 minutes)

    make

- run shorter test (5-10 minutes): highly recommend to run this first

    make test.medium

- run much shorter test (2-5 minutes)

    make test.short

- To debug, you can run simple test

    phenix.AmberPrep 2igd.pdb LES=True clean=False

2. Further info
- Check Makefile
- Check __doc__ in ./run_tests.py
